title: PTLens 8.9
description:
Greetings,

I tested (on XP) several versions in order to upgrade from 8.7.8 version that was missing my lens and this one works!

Best way to upgrade a pirated version is to uninstall the previous one and run a 'regedit' to remove this key: HKLMSoftwareePaperPress before upgrading.

I'm betting the programmer banned the previous license that so many people were using.


Installation is easy: unRar, run the 'install' file, run PTLens (from the destop or start menu, not as a plugin), access the 'help' menu to enter the provided license.



Have a nice day.
